{"tid":1213794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人 打不死 喊夠了 起身再繼續","createTime":"2019-06-13T02:46:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T10:29:07.000Z","uid":12675,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"801789f5cc5521df912f00da98276a0b62ea5df0","tid":1213794,"uid":12675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:46:51.000Z","msg":"經過左6.12 喊左好幾次<br />\n但係唔好放棄 趁住仲有一丁點自由 我地仲可以繼續不合作運動 <br />\n我知道大家好攰 但起碼撐到20/6 因為之後就一定冇自由<br />\n最後通唔通過到 冇人知<br />\n宜家唔好俾d 放棄論影響到！因為你地放棄，就等於放棄左宜家仲努力緊既勇士！<br />\nI love Hong Kong<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">邊個要放棄既就自己搵朋友呻，唔好開post 叫人放棄<br />\n否則一律當3毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"9ffd4db1b6217af6ae3f4e49b386de9145829b29","tid":1213794,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:47:20.000Z","msg":"我相信和理非係有佢嘅威力，倒如全民不合作運動可以對一個政府造成極大經濟壓力，迫佢撤回逃犯條例<br />\n<br />\n全民不合作運動<br />\n<br />\n佔香港大多數嘅和理非可以用一切合法手段，以合法嘅不合作運動反送中，例如教會基督徒可以申請不反對通知書組織一大班人祈禱唱下聖詩，渣車安全起見渣慢啲（要符合道路最低限速要求），全民一齊再楝定一兩日罷工罷市罷課，一班人夾定時間撘多啲火車地鐵參觀香港，宣傳方面可以周街派宣傳反送中單張等等，總之要合法，但又可以喚起社會更多人關注，叧一方面亦同時爭取緊國際支持向政府施加壓力（eg取消美國香港關係法、各國商會嘅反對）去迫政府撤回逃犯條例。"},{"pid":"1cae4e33c277b145182aecfb28d5276fd8ed1ac2","tid":1213794,"uid":12675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:49:15.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9a6f900e51ba7696187a5b0072c46564aa52e305","tid":1213794,"uid":12675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:51:35.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f4ffa8aeced3210d964642044311ced4a2b57d2e","tid":1213794,"uid":12675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:00:17.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"858e148b7854cc1087be85b48fdd5883fa51aa98","tid":1213794,"uid":12675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:04:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c89d2da8097edf5f017414b52d0090036e9599f9","tid":1213794,"uid":12675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:07:01.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a33fe5146900ec38183ea878b0ddb55589049f89","tid":1213794,"uid":12675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:07:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e74a3e34c7ea874bcb299fe693947f4450cf0a37","tid":1213794,"uid":12675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:11:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"10787fc3853378a7bb6b44292f6bcd91cef1c4e2","tid":1213794,"uid":12675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:22:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d5cd447796193d1b22f2a1e7884412f1df9ae49c","tid":1213794,"uid":12675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:38:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"57563b5ed28175404194295d094593c0afabf8da","tid":1213794,"uid":12675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:07:59.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c19419df6b2d1975166fa6ff9c2ab921c3995cf8","tid":1213794,"uid":12675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:29:07.000Z","msg":"push"}]}